 to an outlet           - all other inlets connected to that outlet are disconnecteddisconnect - optional arguments - 2 ints           - disconnects an inlet to an outlet											- the outlet is cleared to the color specified by the clearcolor messageclearcolor - optional argumetns - 3 ints           - specifies the color to be used for the clearscreen when an outlet is switched off